fr.emse.simulator.world

Interface Cell


  • public interface Cell
    A cell is a component of a map. Cells are sorted in a 2-d grid using a (row,column) frame. A cell may contain only an Occupant which is knowned using the getOccupant() method.
    Author:
    Gauthier Picard (SMA/G2I/EMSE) : picard@emse.fr
